<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Mentor Application Approved - Shinobi Open-Source Academy</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #171717;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #0d1b60;
      padding: 24px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .logo {
      max-width: 180px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }

    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #304ffe;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .main-heading {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #171717;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .info-box {
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    }

    .info-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .info-label {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #9e9e9e;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-right: 15px;
    }

    .info-value {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #171717;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: right;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .custom-message-box {
      background-color: rgba(48, 79, 254, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(48, 79, 254, 0.2);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      padding: 25px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    }

    .footer-text {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9e9e9e;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .social-links {
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .social-links a {
      color: #304ffe;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 10px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .contact-info {
      margin-top: 25px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #9e9e9e;
    }

    .contact-info a {
      color: #304ffe;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .reminder-box {
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #171717;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="cid:logo" alt="Shinobi Open-Source Academy" class="logo">
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="greeting">Dear {{name}},</div>

      <div class="main-heading">Congratulations – Your Mentor Application Has Been Approved!</div>

      <p>We are pleased to inform you that your application to become a mentor at <strong>Shinobi Open-Source
          Academy</strong> has been approved. Thank you for your interest in guiding and supporting our community.</p>

      {{#if communityNames}}
      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-row">
          <div class="info-label">Communities you will lead</div>
          <div class="info-value">{{communityNames}}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      {{#if customMessage}}
      <div class="custom-message-box">
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #171717; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">{{customMessage}}</p>
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <p>Next steps: our team will reach out with onboarding details and how to join mentor channels. You will receive
        calendar invites and updates via email.</p>

      <div class="reminder-box">
        <strong>Stay connected:</strong> Follow us on social media and join our Discord to stay updated on events,
        workshops, and community announcements. We also send a weekly digest – please keep an eye on your inbox for
        upcoming events.
      </div>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <p>Questions? Contact us at <a
            href="mailto:contact@shinobi-open-source.academy">contact@shinobi-open-source.academy</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="footer-text">© {{currentYear}} Shinobi Open-Source Academy. All rights reserved.</div>
      <div class="footer-text">You're receiving this email because your mentor application was approved at Shinobi
        Open-Source Academy.</div>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/Shinobi-Open-Source-Academy">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/SOSAcademy_">X (Twitter)</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/shinobi-open-source-academy/">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/X9PWySkvKM">Discord</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
